5:
Okay, everyone!
Today's gift hunt is about to begin!
9:
Find all the presents I've hidden on
your own!
12:
Santa Mia! Give us a map of where
your presents are hidden!
15:
Okay! Just so you know, I ramped up
the difficulty for today's hunt. Good
luck—you'll need it!
18:
And remember, I am not JUST
"Santa Mia," I am the great Treasure
Santa and I request that you
address me as such!
20:
Thank you, Santa Mia! This time I'm
gonna find the most presents!
24:
Oh, come on! Did I not JUST say to
call me Treasure Santa?!
28: You look like you're having fun, Mia.
32:
Why wouldn't I be? I've given
everyone the best gift of all—the joy
of the hunt!
36:
And this Santa work is fun as heck! I
can't wait to hit more locations—
39:
Seriously? SANTA? C'mon, grow up.
Santa isn't real and you know it.
42: B-but, Santa gave me this map...
44:
That's obviously not the real Santa. If
it was, we'd be—
47:
STOP! No fighting allowed, you hear?
That's a surefire way to get on my
naughty list.
50:
Besides, it's the holidays! What could
you possibly have to argue about?
53:
Shut up—and mind your own
business. Whatever... You're all a
bunch of idiots!
56: Whoa, calm down! And come back!
62:
I just want to know why you're so
angry, that's all!
65:
Because everyone is acting like
idiots! Everyone knows Santa isn't
real, but they're all pretending like
he is…
71:
No… And so what? It's got nothin' to
do with you—just leave me alone!
79:
Some proof that Santa is real.
Lucky for you, I've got exactly that!
94:
Now then, climb aboard! Final
boarding call for our solo passenger!
97:
Wh-what the… This thing can FLY?!
Who ARE you?!
103:
You see, at this very moment, WE
are Santa!
107:
You heard me right—that includes
you, too!
110:
Of course, you're still a rookie, but
that doesn't matter! Welcome
aboard, Santa!
124:
We've got lots of work ahead of us!
Let's get to it!
130:
To take care of Santa's single most
important job, of course.
139:
Happy Holidays!
Treasure Santa has presents for all!
142:
This time, Santa's got a little helper
of her own! All right now, form a line!
149:
Now's your time to shine—give out
that present!
152: Thank you for the present, Santa!
156: Santa, Santa! I want a present, too!
159:
Would you look at that? They love
you! Hehe, you'd better not
disappoint your fans, Santa!
163:
We CANNOT allow him to upstage
us, Mia!
166:
You've got that right. We'd better get
to giftin', too!
170:
Who wants a present next? Come
get one from your friendly local
Santas!
174:
All right, on to our next destination!
Where should we go? Got any
requests?
177: I... want to go see my little sister.
179:
I thought Santa would never visit us
again. But if I'M Santa...
182:
Hehe. Now that's what I call holiday
spirit! Consider it done!
194: Hold on to your hats, Santas!
205:
This is a perfect opportunity to
teach you the joy of the hunt!
208:
Our target: your kid sister's
happiness!
